        <Meaning id="a710a3a9-dee3-47eb-bfd4-ffc0096d6297" type="Adjective">
          <Vi>thuộc nông thôn; nông thôn</Vi>
          <En>relating to, occurring in, or characteristic of the countryside or rural areas, especially as opposed to urban or metropolitan areas.</En>
          <Example>The village is a quiet, rural community surrounded by farmland.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="15033c20-d936-47ff-8a28-a9d4610215e6">
