              <En>Describing living conditions or activities in sparsely populated areas with open land and agriculture.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="fb52aeff-4a44-4269-99e2-bd43baef86d8">
              <Vi>So sánh giữa đời sống nông thôn và thành thị.</Vi>
              <En>Contrasting lifestyle, infrastructure, or economic activities between rural and urban settings.</En>
